Egypt is all crying for you .. Sad message from Engi speech to Haitham Ahmed Zaki
07 Nov 2019, 04:33 by Mohamed Badran
Mohamed Badran called the artist Angie Khattab her colleague Haitham Ahmed Zaki, who left the world in the early hours of this morning at the age of 35 years. Haitham Ahmed Zaki began his artistic career In 2006, he completed the rest of the scenes of the film `` Halim '' after the departure of his father, the hero of the film the great artist Ahmed Zaki, to the next year starring the film `` Platacho '', and then continued his works to the end of the series 'question mark' in Ramadan 2019, which is the last of his works .
